Israeli Apartheid Week 2017 is taking place from 5-11 March this year, and as always, it&#8217;s sure to be lit. That&#8217;s mostly because people feel very strongly about which side of the fence (or wall) they sit on when it comes to Israel and Palestine.But what&#8217;s all the fuss about? The Daily Vox unpacks the parallels between the South African apartheid state and Israeli apartheid.